<div class="container" style="text-align:center">
  <h1>
    Welcome to <span style="font-family: allura; font-size: 70px; font-weight: bold;">en root</span>
  </h1>

  <p style="font-size:20px;">An app designed to facilitate the establishment and maintenance of native flora in home gardens.
  The app allows you to browse through a USDA database of plant information to find plants native to your area. Once you've added some plants
  into your garden plots you can see useful information about your garden, such as ideal temperature, pH levels, and moisture levels for your plot.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size:20px;">
  Login and create a garden to get started!
  </p>

